{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b84905a6-5095-43d4-bd97-70e004ff4258",
    "name": "Nexus",
    "description": "Colección Postman para la API de Nexus (panel + Authorization Server OIDC).\n\n## Flujo rápido\n1. Importa esta colección y el environment `Nexus Local`.\n2. Selecciona el environment.\n3. **Auth & Session → Get CSRF token** (el backend emite la cookie XSRF-TOKEN y se guarda el token).\n4. **Create account** → **Login**.\n5. El resto de endpoints ya funcionan: los IDs (account_id, project_id, session_id) y los tokens OIDC se autocompletan desde los test scripts.\n\n## Notas\n- La cabecera `X-XSRF-TOKEN` se inyecta sola desde un pre-request script de la colección (double-submit con la cookie XSRF-TOKEN).\n- La cookie jar de Postman gestiona automáticamente JSESSIONID y XSRF-TOKEN: déjala activada (es el comportamiento por defecto).\n- Variables de configuración (api_base_url, credenciales, cliente OIDC) viven en el environment; las de runtime (csrf_token, ids, tokens) se capturan en variables de la colección.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "var csrf = pm.collectionVariables.get('csrf_token');",
          "if (csrf) {",
          "    try { pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'X-XSRF-TOKEN', value: csrf }); }",
          "    catch (e) { pm.request.headers.add({ key: 'X-XSRF-TOKEN', value: csrf }); }",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    { "key": "csrf_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "account_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "instance_admin", "value": "" },
    { "key": "project_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "session_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "authorization_endpoint", "value": "" },
    { "key": "token_endpoint", "value": "" },
    { "key": "userinfo_endpoint", "value": "" },
    { "key": "jwks_uri", "value": "" },
    { "key": "authorization_code", "value": "" },
    { "key": "access_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_token", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1 · Auth & Session",
      "description": "Alta de cuenta, login, cuenta actual y logout del panel Nexus. Orden recomendado: Get CSRF → Create account → Login.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get CSRF token",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_base_url}}/api/panel/v1/csrf",
            "auth": null,
            "body": null
          },
          "description": "Inicializa la protección CSRF. Devuelve {headerName, parameterName, token} en el cuerpo y deja la cookie XSRF-TOKEN (la cookie jar la reenvía en las escrituras). Ejecuta esto PRIMERO.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('token presente en el cuerpo', () => pm.expect(body.token).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "if (body.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('csrf_token', body.token); console.log('CSRF token guardado'); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Create account",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_base_url}}/api/panel/v1/accounts",
            "auth": null,
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{account_email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{account_password}}\",\n  \"displayName\": \"{{account_display_name}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "description": "Crea una cuenta Nexus (público, sin login). Si ya existe devuelve 409; ignóralo y pasa a Login.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('201 creado o 409 ya existe', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([201, 409]));",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) { const body = pm.response.json(); if (body && body.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('account_id', body.id); console.log('Cuenta creada:', body && body.email); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_base_url}}/api/panel/v1/session/login",
            "auth": null,
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{account_email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{account_password}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "description": "Login JSON del panel. Autentica y establece la sesión (JSESSIONID) que la cookie jar reutiliza. Guarda account_id e instance_admin.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body && body.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('account_id', body.id);",
                  "if (body) pm.collectionVariables.set('instance_admin', String(body.instanceAdmin));",
                  "console.log('Login correcto como', body && body.email, '| instanceAdmin =', body && body.instanceAdmin);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Current account (me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_base_url}}/api/panel/v1/me",
            "auth": null,
            "body": null
          },
          "description": "Devuelve la cuenta autenticada. Útil para comprobar que la sesión está activa.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_base_url}}/api/panel/v1/session/logout",
            "auth": null,
            "body": null
          },
          "description": "Cierra la sesión actual (204). Después necesitarás Login de nuevo para los endpoints protegidos.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('204 No Content', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(204));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2 · Projects",
      "description": "Ciclo de vida de proyectos: crear, listar y obtener por id.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create project",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_base_url}}/api/panel/v1/projects",
            "auth": null,
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"slug\": \"{{project_slug}}\",\n  \"name\": \"{{project_name}}\",\n  \"description\": \"Proyecto de prueba creado desde Postman\",\n  \"publicBaseUrl\": \"https://{{project_slug}}.nexus.local\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "description": "Crea un proyecto y guarda su id en project_id.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body && body.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('project_id', body.id);",
                  "if (body && body.slug) pm.collectionVariables.set('project_slug', body.slug);",
                  "console.log('Proyecto creado:', body && body.name, '→ project_id =', body && body.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "List accessible projects",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_base_url}}/api/panel/v1/projects",
            "auth": null,
            "body": null
          },
          "description": "Lista los proyectos accesibles (los del usuario o todos si es instanceAdmin).",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (Array.isArray(body) && body.length && !pm.collectionVariables.get('project_id')) { pm.collectionVariables.set('project_id', body[0].id); console.log('project_id fijado:', body[0].id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Get project by id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_base_url}}/api/panel/v1/projects/{{project_id}}",
            "auth": null,
            "body": null
          },
          "description": "Detalle de un proyecto. Requiere acceso (miembro o instanceAdmin).",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3 · Sessions",
      "description": "Gestión de sesiones del panel: listar, revocar una o revocar todas.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List sessions",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_base_url}}/api/panel/v1/sessions",
            "auth": null,
            "body": null
          },
          "description": "Lista las sesiones del panel de la cuenta (la actual primero). Guarda el id de una sesión revocable en session_id.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (Array.isArray(body) && body.length) { const other = body.find(s => !s.current) || body[0]; if (other && other.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('session_id', other.id); console.log('Sesiones:', body.length, '| session_id =', other && other.id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Revoke one session",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_base_url}}/api/panel/v1/sessions/{{session_id}}",
            "auth": null,
            "body": null
          },
          "description": "Revoca la sesión session_id (204). Si es la actual, también te desloguea.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('204 No Content', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(204));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Revoke all sessions",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_base_url}}/api/panel/v1/sessions",
            "auth": null,
            "body": null
          },
          "description": "Revoca TODAS las sesiones incluida la actual (204). Tras esto necesitas Login de nuevo.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('204 No Content', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(204));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4 · OIDC / OAuth",
      "description": "Flujo OIDC del Authorization Server de Nexus. El panel Next.js NO usa este cliente; autentica por sesión HTTP en /api/panel/v1/session/login.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Discovery",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_base_url}}/.well-known/openid-configuration",
            "auth": null,
            "body": null
          },
          "description": "Descubre los endpoints OIDC del Authorization Server y los guarda en variables.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('authorization_endpoint', body.authorization_endpoint);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('token_endpoint', body.token_endpoint);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('userinfo_endpoint', body.userinfo_endpoint);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('jwks_uri', body.jwks_uri);",
                  "console.log('Endpoints OIDC guardados');"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Authorize (browser)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{authorization_endpoint}}?response_type=code&client_id={{client_id}}&scope={{scope}}&redirect_uri={{redirect_uri}}&state={{state}}&nonce={{nonce}}",
            "auth": null,
            "body": null
          },
          "description": "Abre login/consent en el navegador. Tras autorizar, copia el valor de ?code=... de la URL de redirección y pégalo en la variable authorization_code."
        },
        {
          "name": "Token (authorization_code)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{token_endpoint}}",
            "auth": {
              "type": "basic",
              "basic": [
                { "key": "username", "value": "{{client_id}}", "type": "string" },
                { "key": "password", "value": "{{client_secret}}", "type": "string" }
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                { "key": "grant_type", "value": "authorization_code", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "code", "value": "{{authorization_code}}", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "redirect_uri", "value": "{{redirect_uri}}", "type": "text" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "description": "Intercambia el authorization_code por access_token, id_token y refresh_token.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body.access_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', body.access_token);",
                  "if (body.refresh_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', body.refresh_token);",
                  "if (body.id_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('id_token', body.id_token);",
                  "console.log('Tokens guardados');"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "UserInfo",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{userinfo_endpoint}}",
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                { "key": "token", "value": "{{access_token}}", "type": "string" }
              ]
            },
            "body": null
          },
          "description": "Consulta claims de usuario con el access token.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Token (refresh_token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{token_endpoint}}",
            "auth": {
              "type": "basic",
              "basic": [
                { "key": "username", "value": "{{client_id}}", "type": "string" },
                { "key": "password", "value": "{{client_secret}}", "type": "string" }
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                { "key": "grant_type", "value": "refresh_token", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "{{refresh_token}}", "type": "text" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "description": "Renueva el access token usando el refresh token.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body.access_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', body.access_token);",
                  "if (body.refresh_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', body.refresh_token);",
                  "console.log('Tokens renovados');"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "JWKS",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{jwks_uri}}",
            "auth": null,
            "body": null
          },
          "description": "Claves públicas del Authorization Server.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
